Flying, ward {2}
[i]Astra Blade[/i] – Whenever Catria, Mild Middle Sister attacks, if you are attacking with two other Pegasi, she gains double strike until end of turn.
[i]Sisterhood[/i] – If you control a creature named Est and a creature named Palla, Pegasi you control have “Crit – Whenever this creature deals combat damage to a player, return target nonland permanent to its owner's hand.”
